legislation: European Union (Definition of Treaties) (Stabilisation and Association Agreement) (Bosnia and Herzegovina) Order 2010
description: Letter dated 11/03/2010 from Lord Brett to Lord Hylton regarding European Union (Definition of Treaties) (Stabilisation and Association Agreement) (Bosnia and Herzegovina) Order 2010, asymmetrical trade preferences, the length of the transitional period for the free trade area and benefits for Bosnia. 2 p.
